*To make a Pod*
kubectl run ayush  --image=nginx/httpd -n prod

*To make a deployment*
kubectl create deployment ayush-deploy --image=nginx/httpd -n prod

*To crete a service*
kubectl expose deployment ayush-deploy --port=80 --target-port=80 -n prod

*To see logs*
kubectl logs pod/ayush -n prod

*To see running pods functions/when a pod is stucked on ImagePullBackOff error*
kubectl describe pod/ayush -n prod
kubectl describe ayush -n prod

*To forward the port of the service*
kubectl port-forward ayush-deploy 8080:80 -n prod


